Name: Antitetrise
About the game: Play old game genre with new mechanics: tiles will disappear only when you build outline with them. Stick figure to figure, move throught bounds and get points only for new figures. Try to find a strategy against fully random figures from scattered tiles or be not confused in double-screen mode.
